Thursday's earthquake happened almost 60km off the coast of Fukushima, not far from the epicentre of the most powerful earthquake in Japan's history, which killed 18,000 people when it struck 11 years ago.

1.看逗號,劃動詞介系詞分短句
Thursday's earthquake happened almost 60km off the coast of Fukushima
                      ^^^^^^^^
週四的地震發生距離福島海岸約60公里處

2.not far from the epicentre of the most powerful earthquake in Japan's history
      ^^^^^^^^
距離日本史上最強烈地震的震央不遠

3.which killed 18,000 people when it struck 11 years ago
11年前襲擊的最強烈地震,造成18000人死亡.

4.整句=> 週四的地震發生距離福島海岸約60公里處,距離日本史上最強烈地震的震央不遠,那次地震在11前襲擊,造成18000人死亡.   

The 2011 earthquake triggered a tsunami and destroyed the Fukushima nuclear plant,/sparking a major disaster after radiation leaked from the plant.
                    ^^^^^^^^^               ^^^^^^^^^                              ^^^^^^^^
1.The 2011 earthquake triggered a tsunami and destroyed the Fukushima nuclear plant
                      ^^^^^^^^^           ^^^ ^^^^^^^^^ 
2011年的地震引發了海嘯並且摧毀了福島核電廠，                                  

2.sparking a major disaster after radiation leaked from the plant.
  ^^^^^^^^
輻射從核電廠洩漏後,引發重大災難.

3.整句=>2011年的地震引發了海嘯並且摧毀了福島核電廠，輻射從核電廠洩漏後,引發重大災難.

Nuclear authorities said /that no abnormalities had been detected /after Wednesday night's earthquake at the damaged Fukushima site.
                         ^^^^^                  ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^  ^^^^^
1.Nuclear authorities said =>核電機關當局說

2.that no abnormalities had been detected=>沒有偵測到異常 

3.after Wednesday night's earthquake at the damaged Fukushima site.=>週三晚上在受損的福島遺址發生地震後

4.整句=>核電機關當局表示,週三晚上發生地震後,在受損的福島遺址沒有偵測到異常